        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[开发者很好说话的，不需要使用敬辞/doge，大家可以跟开发者开无限制的玩笑/doge，别有太大的隔阂哈...]]></summary>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>开发者很好说话的，不需要使用敬辞<img loading="lazy" alt="/doge" src="data:image/png;base64," width="28" height="28" class="img_ev3q">，大家可以跟开发者开无限制的玩笑<img loading="lazy" alt="/doge" src="data:image/png;base64," width="28" height="28" class="img_ev3q">，别有太大的隔阂哈...</p><p>“请”，“您”，对我来说太惊悚了</p><div class="theme-admonition theme-admonition-danger alert alert--danger admonition_LlT9"><div class="admonitionHeading_tbUL"><span class="admonitionIcon_kALy"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.05.31c.81 2.17.41 3.38-.52 4.31C3.55 5.67 1.98 6.45.9 7.98c-1.45 2.05-1.7 6.53 3.53 7.7-2.2-1.16-2.67-4.52-.3-6.61-.61 2.03.53 3.33 1.94 2.86 1.39-.47 2.3.53 2.27 1.67-.02.78-.31 1.44-1.13 1.81 3.42-.59 4.78-3.42 4.78-5.56 0-2.84-2.53-3.22-1.25-5.61-1.52.13-2.03 1.13-1.89 2.75.09 1.08-1.02 1.8-1.86 1.33-.67-.41-.66-1.19-.06-1.78C8.18 5.31 8.68 2.45 5.05.32L5.03.3l.02.01z"></path></svg></span>危险</div><div class="admonitionContent_S0QG"><h4 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="错误示范上">错误示范（上）：<a class="hash-link" href="#错误示范上" title="标题的直接链接">​</a></h4><p>您好，在吗？不好意思打扰您了，想来问个问题可以吗？麻烦您了。</p><blockquote><p>我的评价是：别别别，承受不住</p></blockquote></div></div><div class="theme-admonition theme-admonition-caution alert alert--warning admonition_LlT9"><div class="admonitionHeading_tbUL"><span class="admonitionIcon_kALy"><svg viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.893 1.5c-.183-.31-.52-.5-.887-.5s-.703.19-.886.5L.138 13.499a.98.98 0 0 0 0 1.001c.193.31.53.501.886.501h13.964c.367 0 .704-.19.877-.5a1.03 1.03 0 0 0 .01-1.002L8.893 1.5zm.133 11.497H6.987v-2.003h2.039v2.003zm0-3.004H6.987V5.987h2.039v4.006z"></path></svg></span>警告</div><div class="admonitionContent_S0QG"><h4 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="错误示范中">错误示范（中）：<a class="hash-link" href="#错误示范中" title="标题的直接链接">​</a></h4><p>在不在，问个问题</p><blockquote><p>我的评价是：问啥啊</p></blockquote></div></div><div class="theme-admonition theme-admonition-tip alert alert--success admonition_LlT9"><div class="admonitionHeading_tbUL"><span class="admonitionIcon_kALy"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M6.5 0C3.48 0 1 2.19 1 5c0 .92.55 2.25 1 3 1.34 2.25 1.78 2.78 2 4v1h5v-1c.22-1.22.66-1.75 2-4 .45-.75 1-2.08 1-3 0-2.81-2.48-5-5.5-5zm3.64 7.48c-.25.44-.47.8-.67 1.11-.86 1.41-1.25 2.06-1.45 3.23-.02.05-.02.11-.02.17H5c0-.06 0-.13-.02-.17-.2-1.17-.59-1.83-1.45-3.23-.2-.31-.42-.67-.67-1.11C2.44 6.78 2 5.65 2 5c0-2.2 2.02-4 4.5-4 1.22 0 2.36.42 3.22 1.19C10.55 2.94 11 3.94 11 5c0 .66-.44 1.78-.86 2.48zM4 14h5c-.23 1.14-1.3 2-2.5 2s-2.27-.86-2.5-2z"></path></svg></span>提示</div><div class="admonitionContent_S0QG"><h4 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="正确示范">正确示范<a class="hash-link" href="#正确示范" title="标题的直接链接">​</a></h4><p>我WebDav登录失败怎么办？（附上操作视频/截图）</p><blockquote><p>我的评价是：太美丽了，就喜欢这样的用户<img loading="lazy" alt="/doge" src="data:image/png;base64," width="28" height="28" class="img_ev3q"></p></blockquote></div></div><p><a href="https://pd.qq.com/s/61vf6d5qi" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">官方频道 点击加入QQ频道【VideoYou】</a></p><p>欸嘿</p>]]></content>
